OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has warned that
OL,8,Fcombating the effects of the ongoing
OL,9,Fwar in Iran "will not be easy" and
OL,10,F"will affect the future of our
OL,11,Fcountry".
OL,13,FSpeaking at a Downing Street press
OL,14,Fconference on Wednesday, the PM set
OL,15,Fout a series of measures his
OL,16,Fgovernment had already brought in to
OL,17,Fsupport people with the cost of living.
OL,26,@sD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FStarmer insisted the UK was "well-
OL,8,Fplaced" to weather the storm as the
OL,9,Fconflict hits the economy and pushes
OL,10,Fup fuel and energy costs for consumers.
OL,12,FHe also highlighted the "deep damage
OL,13,Fto our economy" Brexit had done, as he
OL,14,Fpledged closer alignment with the
OL,15,FEuropean bloc.
OL,17,F'Well-placed' to weather the storm
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FStarmer's words come against a
OL,8,Fbackdrop of the war in the Middle East
OL,9,Fand the continued blockade of the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, which has pushed up
OL,11,Fpetrol prices to their highest level
OL,12,Fsince 2023.
OL,14,FAddressing reporters, the prime
OL,15,Fminister highlighted a set of measures
OL,16,Fthe government was already taking to
OL,17,Fcombat the rising cost-of-living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThese included cutting energy bills by
OL,8,Fover #100 per household, extending the
OL,9,Fcut in fuel duty until September, a
OL,10,F#53 million support package for
OL,11,Fconsumers relying on heating oil, and
OL,12,Finvestments in renewable energy.
OL,14,F"I'm sick and tired of your energy
OL,15,Fbills fluctuating up and down because
OL,16,Fwe're on the international market," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"If we took control of our energy and
OL,20,Fhad homegrown renewables, we could
OL,21,Fstabilise your bills."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThe prime minister also pointed to
OL,8,Fseveral other measures Labour had
OL,9,Ftaken since taking office to address
OL,10,Fcosts for consumers, including frozen
OL,11,Fprescription prices, rising national
OL,12,Fliving wages, a rising state pension,
OL,13,Fand scrapping the two-child benefit
OL,14,Fcap.
OL,16,FThe prime minister maintained that de-
OL,17,Fescalation in Iran remained the best
OL,18,Fway to bring down costs for UK
OL,19,Fconsumers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FTo this end, Starmer announced that
OL,8,Flater this week, the Foreign Secretary
OL,9,FYvette Cooper will host a meeting of
OL,10,Finternational partners to discuss how
OL,11,Fbest to ease tensions.
OL,13,F"Following that meeting, we will also
OL,14,Fconvene our military planners to look
OL,15,Fat how we can marshal our capabilities
OL,16,Fand make the Strait accessible and
OL,17,Fsafe," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,F"Whatever the pressure on me and
OL,8,Fothers, whatever the noise, I'm going
OL,9,Fto act in the British national
OL,10,Finterest," the PM said
OL,12,FA closer EU partnership
OL,14,FStarmer emphasised the need for
OL,15,F"closer economic cooperation" with
OL,16,FEurope, after Brexit caused "deep
OL,17,Fdamage to our economy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FHe continued: "The opportunities to
OL,8,Fstrengthen our security and cut the
OL,9,Fcost of living are simply too big to
OL,10,Fignore."
OL,12,FThe prime minister announced that the
OL,13,FUK would seek a new partnership with
OL,14,Fthe EU, participating in a summit in
OL,15,Fthe coming weeks to establish
OL,16,F"economic cooperation" and "security
OL,17,Fcooperation".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FAsked whether Labour's manifesto red
OL,8,Flines on closer relations with Europe
OL,9,Fremain, Starmer insisted they did,
OL,10,Fdenying he was choosing EU partners
OL,11,Fover the special relationship with the
OL,12,FUS.
OL,14,F"The manifesto commitments remain, but
OL,15,Fwe made it clear in the manifesto that
OL,16,Fwe wanted a closer relationship with
OL,17,FEurope, so that is perfectly
OL,18,Fconsistent with our manifesto.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,F"I think it is in our interest to have
OL,8,Fa strong relationship with the US and
OL,9,Fwith Europe. But I do think that when
OL,10,Fit comes to defence and security,
OL,11,Fenergy emissions, and the economy, we
OL,12,Fneed a stronger relationship with
OL,13,FEurope.
OL,15,F"I actually think that will help
OL,16,Fstrengthen our relationship with the
OL,17,FUS, because successive presidents have
OL,18,Fsaid that Europe needs to do more on
OL,19,Ftheir defence and security."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
