OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHelp is coming, but not for everyone,
OL,13,Fand not yet
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThe Chancellor Rachel Reeves had
OL,8,Falready told ITV News that further
OL,9,Fhelp would come, but that it would be
OL,10,Ftargeted at those most in need, with
OL,11,Fthe government using the following
OL,12,Fthree months of cheaper energy bills,
OL,13,Fthanks to a falling price cap, to
OL,14,Fassess what was needed.
OL,16,F"We're using this time we have to work
OL,17,Fthrough all the different
OL,18,Fcontingencies and different options,
OL,19,Ffor more tailored and targeted
OL,20,Fsupport," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,F"What we've done so far is reducing
OL,8,Fcosts for everybody's prescriptions,
OL,9,Ftrains, and of course, most of all on
OL,10,Fenergy bills," she said. "But we're
OL,11,Flooking at what else might be needed."
OL,13,F"This will not be easy," said Starmer
OL,14,Fas he set out some of the measures
OL,15,FLabour are taking to insulate the UK
OL,16,Ffrom the effects of the war in Iran
OL,18,FSome bills set to rise
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FResponding to Labour's claims of
OL,8,Ftackling the cost-of-living, the
OL,9,FConservatives argued the opposite,
OL,10,Fhighlighting several bills set to rise
OL,11,Ffor consumers instead.
OL,13,F"Despite promising to put the cost of
OL,14,Fliving first, Keir Starmer and his
OL,15,FChancellor have piled on extra costs,
OL,16,Fleaving families almost #1,000 worse
OL,17,Foff this year," the Conservatives said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Fsaid: "Keir Starmer and Rachel Reeves
OL,9,Fclaim they care about the cost of
OL,10,Fliving, but today they are hammering
OL,11,Ffamilies with new taxes and rising
OL,12,Fcharges, and businesses with new
OL,13,Fregulations and red tape.
OL,15,F"Since Labour came in, they have done
OL,16,Fnothing but make life harder for
OL,17,Fworking families and the small
OL,18,Fbusinesses that power our country.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, they hand out more and more
OL,20,Fto those on benefits.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775067061
OL,3,C'This will not be easy' says PM,
OL,4,Csetting out plans to counter impact of
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,F"Labour have no plan to fix the mess
OL,8,Fthey have created. The Conservatives
OL,9,Fare the only party who will get
OL,10,FBritain working again and deliver a
OL,11,FStronger Economy and Stronger Country."
OL,13,FWhilst Ofgem's price cap will see
OL,14,Fconsumer's energy bills fall by around
OL,15,F7%, the latest predictions see these
OL,16,Frising by around #300 in three months
OL,17,Ftime when the effect of the war begins
OL,18,Fto show in energy prices.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
